---
// Results & Impact — Sama (featured/dark), C2FO, Fundbox
---

<section id="results">
  <span class="section-label">Results &amp; Impact</span>
  <h2 class="section-title reveal">A career built on <em>measurable outcomes</em></h2>
  <p class="results-intro reveal">
    From doubling organic traffic to earning an industry award — these are the
    numbers and moments that define the work.
  </p>

  <div class="results-grid">

    <!-- Sama — featured dark card (award, no metric stat) -->
    <div class="rcard rcard--featured reveal">
      <div class="rcard-inner">
        <div class="rcard-left">
          <span class="rcard-company">Sama (Samasource)</span>
          <h3 class="rcard-title">Award-winning AI case study</h3>
          <p class="rcard-body">
            Built the content program that helped Sama communicate the complexity
            and value of machine learning data labelling to enterprise buyers. Led
            development of a customer advocacy content series — the Vulcan wildlife
            conservation story — that earned Sama recognition at the 2020 AI
            Breakthrough Awards.
          </p>
          <a
            href="https://www.sama.com/blog/how-vulcan-is-using-ai-for-wildlife-conservation"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="rcard-link"
          >
            Read the case study →
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="rcard-award">
          <span class="award-label">Award Winner</span>
          <p class="award-name">2020 AI Breakthrough Award</p>
          <span class="award-org">Artificial Intelligence<br/>Breakthrough Awards</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- C2FO -->
    <div class="rcard reveal delay-1">
      <span class="rcard-stat">2×</span>
      <span class="rcard-company">C2FO · Working Capital Platform</span>
      <h3 class="rcard-title">Organic search doubled in 12 months</h3>
      <p class="rcard-body">
        Led topic cluster strategy that grew organic traffic from 15% to 32% of
        all site visits, overtaking email as the top channel. Individual articles
        moved from single-digit daily visits to 30–60+ with featured snippets on
        high-intent financial search terms.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Fundbox -->
    <div class="rcard reveal delay-2">
      <span class="rcard-stat">49%</span>
      <span class="rcard-company">Fundbox · SMB FinTech</span>
      <h3 class="rcard-title">Social-to-blog traffic lift</h3>
      <p class="rcard-body">
        Consolidated 20+ independent contributors into a streamlined in-house
        content studio. 113 posts in 9 months, 49% lift in social-to-blog traffic
        and a +91 position jump on a primary keyword.
      </p>
      <p class="rcard-note">
        Built before AI-assisted production. Pure editorial systems thinking.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
section {
  background: var(--cream);
}

.results-intro {
  font-size: 0.97rem;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  line-height: 1.85;
  max-width: 540px;
  margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  font-weight: 300;
}

/* Grid: featured card spans full width on top, two stat cards below */
.results-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5px;
  background: var(--border);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  max-width: 960px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Base card */
.rcard {
  background: var(--warm-white);
  padding: 2.8rem 2.6rem;
  transition: background 0.2s ease;
}
.rcard:hover { background: var(--rose-whisper); }

/* Featured card spans both columns */
.rcard--featured {
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
  background: var(--dark-bg);
  color: #f5ede9;
}
.rcard--featured:hover { background: var(--dark-mid); }

.rcard-inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  gap: 3rem;
  align-items: start;
}

.rcard-left { max-width: 600px; }

/* Stat number (C2FO, Fundbox) */
.rcard-stat {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--rose-blush);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}

.rcard-company {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.62rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--rose-mid);
  margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
}
.rcard--featured .rcard-company { color: rgba(232, 196, 188, 0.65); }

.rcard-title {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--ink);
  line-height: 1.25;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}
.rcard--featured .rcard-title { color: #f5ede9; }

.rcard-body {
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  line-height: 1.82;
  font-weight: 300;
}
.rcard--featured .rcard-body { color: rgba(245, 237, 233, 0.72); }

.rcard-note {
  margin-top: 1rem;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-style: italic;
  font-family: var(--serif);
  color: var(--ink-muted);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.rcard-link {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 1.4rem;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--rose-mid);
  text-decoration: none;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201, 144, 138, 0.4);
  padding-bottom: 0.15rem;
  transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
}
.rcard-link:hover { color: var(--rose-blush); border-color: var(--rose-blush); }

/* Award box */
.rcard-award {
  border: 1px solid rgba(201, 144, 138, 0.25);
  background: rgba(181, 112, 106, 0.1);
  padding: 1.8rem 1.6rem;
  text-align: center;
  min-width: 180px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.award-label {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.58rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--rose-mid);
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}

.award-name {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: #f5ede9;
  line-height: 1.25;
  margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
}

.award-org {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  color: rgba(245, 237, 233, 0.45);
  line-height: 1.5;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
}

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .results-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .rcard-inner  { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.8rem; }
  .rcard-award  { min-width: unset; }
}
</style>
